tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE SecurityEventLogs ( 
    event_id INT PRIMARY KEY, 
    event_type VARCHAR(50), 
    timestamp TIMESTAMP, 
    user_id INT, 
    ip_address VARCHAR(15) 
);

CREATE TABLE SecurityEvents (
  event_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  event_type VARCHAR(50),
  event_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  event_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE DatabaseLogs (
  log_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  log_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  log_level VARCHAR(20),
  log_message TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE IncidentManagement (
  incident_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  incident_type VARCHAR(50),
  incident_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  incident_description TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE IncidentResolution (
  resolution_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  incident_id UUID,
  resolution_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  resolution_details TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE IncidentParticipants (
  participant_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
  participant_name VARCHAR(50),
  participant_role VARCHAR(50),
  participant_contact VARCHAR(50)
)
